def FLATTEN(df_train):
    N = df_train.shape[0]//18
    FLATTEN = np.array(df_train.iloc[:18])
    for i in range(1,N):
        FLATTEN = np.hstack((FLATTEN, df_train.iloc[18*i:18*(i+1)]))
    df_FLATTEN = pd.DataFrame(FLATTEN)
    return df_FLATTEN
In [5]:
df_Tr = FLATTEN(df_train)
df_Te = FLATTEN(df_test)

In [7]:
symbol_list = ['#', '*', 'x', 'A']
def FILLAVE(df_FLATTEN):
    for a in range(0,len(df_FLATTEN)):
        for i in range(1,len(df_FLATTEN.columns)-1):
            j = i-1
            k = i+1
            if sum([str(df_FLATTEN.iloc[a,i]).rfind(sym) for sym in symbol_list])!=-4:
                while sum([str(df_FLATTEN.iloc[a,j]).rfind(sym) for sym in symbol_list])!=-4:
                    j = j-1
                while sum([str(df_FLATTEN.iloc[a,k]).rfind(sym) for sym in symbol_list])!=-4:
                    k = k+1
                    if k>=len(df_FLATTEN.columns)-1: # prediction
                        k=j
                df_FLATTEN.iloc[a,i] = str((float(df_FLATTEN.iloc[a,j]) + float(df_FLATTEN.iloc[a,k]))/2)
        ## new add in 1117
        if sum([1 for sym in symbol_list if sym in df_FLATTEN.iloc[a,-1]])!=0:
            df_FLATTEN.iloc[a,-1] = df_FLATTEN.iloc[a,-2]
    return df_FLATTEN

df_Train = FILLAVE(df_Tr)
df_Test = FILLAVE(df_Te)

def SPDA(df_Train, period, pred, feature=0):
    length = len(df_Train.columns) - pred
    train_x = [ [] for i in range(length)]
    if feature!=1:
        Index = df_Train.index
    else:
        Index = [9]
    for i in range(length):
        for j in Index:
            train_x[i].append(df_Train.loc[j, i:i+period-1])
    train_x = np.float64(train_x).reshape((len(train_x),-1))            
    train_y = np.float64(list(df_Train.loc[9,pred:])).reshape(len(df_Train.loc[9,pred:]),1)
    return train_x, train_y

train1_X_6_p6, train_Y_p6 = SPDA(df_Train, period=6, pred=6, feature=1)
train1_X_6_p11, train_Y_p11 = SPDA(df_Train, period=6, pred=11, feature=1)
train18_X_6_p6, train_Y_p6 = SPDA(df_Train, period=6, pred=6, feature=0)
train18_X_6_p11, train_Y_p11 = SPDA(df_Train, period=6, pred=11, feature=0)

test1_X_6_p6, test_Y_p6 = SPDA(df_Test, period=6, pred=6, feature=1)
test1_X_6_p11, test_Y_p11 = SPDA(df_Test, period=6, pred=11, feature=1)
test18_X_6_p6, test_Y_p6 = SPDA(df_Test, period=6, pred=6, feature=0)
test18_X_6_p11, test_Y_p11 = SPDA(df_Test, period=6, pred=11, feature=0)

Visualize Function¶

In [ ]:
def Plot_the_result(pred_Y, test_Y, hour=10, name='LinearRegression'):
    figsize = (12,4)
    fontsize = 12
    mean_pred_Y = [np.mean(pred_Y[24*i:24*(i+1)]) for i in range(31)]
    mean_test_Y = [np.mean(test_Y[24*i:24*(i+1)]) for i in range(31)]
    x = np.arange(1,len(pred_Y[hour:-1:24])+1)
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=figsize)
    plt.title(f'The prediction of the PM2.5 measurement in Dec. in each days at time {hour:02d}:00.',{"fontsize" : fontsize})
    plt.ylabel('Measure of PM2.5',{"fontsize" : fontsize})
    plt.xlabel(f'Method : {name}' ,{"fontsize" : fontsize})
    plt.xticks(x)
    plt.plot(x, pred_Y[hour:-1:24], color='blue', marker='*', linestyle = 'dashed')
    plt.plot(x, test_Y[hour:-1:24], color='red', marker='o')
    plt.plot(x, mean_pred_Y, color='green', marker='*', linestyle = 'dashed')
    plt.plot(x, mean_test_Y, color='orange', marker='o')
    plt.legend(['pred','real', 'M_pred','M_real'],fontsize=10)
    plt.grid()

namelst = ['predict 6-th(1 feature)','predict 6-th(18 features)', 'predict 11-th(1 feature)','predict 11-th(18 features)']
loss = []
for idx,lst in enumerate(data_list):
    train_X, train_Y, test_X, test_Y = lst
    lr_model = LinearRegression()
    lr_model.fit(train_X, train_Y)
    pred_Y = lr_model.predict(test_X)
    MAE = mean_absolute_error(test_Y, pred_Y)
    Plot_the_result(pred_Y, test_Y, hour=10, name=namelst[idx])
    loss.append(MAE)
print('The MAE(mean absolute error) is')
print(loss)
